{"tid":1502331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[哎呀慘豬] TVB女記者一度被警員包圍查證","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T07:32:42.000Z","uid":24050,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7987a13896ff9d94a7c59744e0074c9447a14b72","tid":1502331,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"【TVB女記者一度被警員包圍查證】<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上10時半，在深水埗警署附近的欽州街，向示威者方向快速推進，示威者後退至鴨寮街等內街。現場警員其後在近晚上11時返回警署內。<br />\n<br />\n警員推進期間，有一名警員用警棍指向身穿記者反光背心的無綫電視女記者。幾名警員其後包圍該名記者，叫她不要動，又要求其他記者讓開。該名女記者及其他記者表明身份，質疑警方為何拘捕記者。該名女記者在警方傳媒聯絡隊檢查記者證後獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台<br />\n#香港警察<br />\n#無綫電視<br />\n#TVB<br />\n<br />\nSource: 香港電台視像新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/posts/2757003924407646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fposts%2F2757003924407646&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84msgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=d3b074e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/posts/2757003924407646</a>"},{"pid":"e660619a60450ab573ba9a7e532ec96fe8fdfc71","tid":1502331,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d0f8d24aaa7fcdf44649f13a63eb28f9843e795e","tid":1502331,"uid":24050,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"無綫新聞提都無提喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女記者有無覺得後悔 寧願做東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ea1a2e1bb3aa5d405d0059dce6fd1d7bc3d985","tid":1502331,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f